window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The strategies for achieving a successful marriage can be compared to the strategies that businesses and entrepreneurs use to achieve success. Being well-prepared for future challenges, developing effective communication skills, demonstrating unity and understanding, and working to be flexible and open to change are just some of the ways that couples can work together to create a positive and rewarding relationship that will stand the test of time. </p> <p>In this audiobook, hear about some of the important things people should know before and during marriage. The marriage contract is all about working together toward success!</p>"; 
